{
  "stem": "13251.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He'd say, a movie?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He'd think he was real-- it was a riot, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He'd think he was real funny.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He'd say, yeah, you can see a movie in bed, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He used to tease the hell out of us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And when he did let us go to the movie, of course, that's-- in those days every movie had a news reel, like 15, 20 minutes, and it gives you a pretty good idea.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was not commercial.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Like here, news is commercial.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was strictly documentary, and it would update you what's going on in the war, as far as what's going on.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And of course radio.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Radio-- religiously you would listen to radio news, always.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was TV there, but radio was very, very-- everybody listened to news, always.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, nothing at all until after the war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I think it was-- I found out afterwards.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- it was known, but it was-- it never seemed to have been an issue.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like it was-- the news media didn't seem to do a much about it, yet it was no secret.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I understand it started-- a concentration camp started way back before the war, you know, in Germany and places like that, not in Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But Hitler started his concentration camps way before the war.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's just the world didn't seem to make an issue of it for some reason.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The news media didn't.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Politics, I guess.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, even Chamberlain tried to appease Hitler, didn't he?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, he offered Czechoslovakia as a gift, like it was his to give Czechoslovakian to, to Germany to appease Hitler.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "What did they-- what did you-- what did the kids think about it?",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
